**Try-with-resources pattern (AutoCloseable wrapper):**
```java
class PooledResource<T> implements AutoCloseable {
    private final T resource;
    private final ObjectPool<T> pool;
    PooledResource(T r, ObjectPool<T> p) { resource = r; pool = p; }
    public T get() { return resource; }
    @Override public void close() { pool.returnToPool(resource); }
}
